title: High-rise blaze at Gunwharf Quays is brought under control
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device High-rise blaze at Gunwharf Quays is brought under control 25 February 2017 Last updated at 15:50 GMT 
Firefighters have been tackling a large fire in a high-rise building in the Gunwharf Quays area of Portsmouth. 
The latest reports are that the fire is out but people remain stranded on the roof of the building. Read more
